  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the pressure cooker over medium-high heat.",
    "Brown the beef short ribs on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and minced garlic to the pressure cooker and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the water, Syrian five spice powder, salt, and black pepper to the pressure cooker.",
    "Close the pressure cooker and cook at high pressure for 30 minutes.",
    "Let the pressure release naturally for 10 minutes, then quick-release any remaining pressure.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
